<HEADLINE>
<P>
JESSE JACKSON'S ROLE IN RELEASE OF HOSTAGES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I feel it is time for the U.S. government to impose some restrictions on 
private citizens such as Jackson from pursuing their own personal foreign 
policy. Jackson doesn't seem to realize that if a player continues to carry the 
ball by himself to exploit his own ambitions, it eventually reduces the 
effectiveness of the team as a whole and causes a strong resentment among other 
players. 
</P>
<P>
JOHN ERICKSON 
</P>
<P>
Ontario 
</P>
