Photo, Gen. Colin Powell, left, visits Marines near the Saudi-Kuwaiti border. 
Associated Press; Photo, A Bedouin pours tea for a U.S. serviceman in one of 
few examples of Saudi and Western cultures mixing. Reuters 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
