Bowl receiver caught 156 passes the last two seasons. Associated Press; Photo, 
(Orange County Edition) COLOR, Henry Ellard, facing Bears here, fumbled three 
of his six receptions against Green Bay Sunday. CHRISTINE COTTER / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, (A2) Three-Peat: The Rams know reliable Henry Ellard won't repeat 
his inexplicable performance of last Sunday, when he fumbled three times 
against the Packers. 
</P>
