<P>
An illegal immigrant identified two of three men Thursday from the San Diego 
Job Corps program as the ones who had robbed him Aug. 30. 
</P>
<P>
The man testified at the preliminary hearing for the men, who are charged with 
robbing seven undocumented workers and trying to rob four others near the 
